Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:41.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}顔を合わしたら喧嘩してばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:47.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それもいい思い出だった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:56.63,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きみが教えてくれたんだ　もう恐くない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:22:09.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな不自由でも幸せは掴める　だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:20.58,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとりでもゆくよ　例え辛くても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:28.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きみと見た夢は　必ず持ってくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:36.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きみとがよかった　ほかの誰もでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:44.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}でも目覚めた朝　きみは居ないんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:09.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと遊んでれる　そんな気がしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:15.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がしていただけ　わかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:24.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生まれてきたこともう後悔はしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:37.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}祭りの後みたい　寂しいけどそろそろ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:48.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでもゆくよ　ここで知ったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:56.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せという夢を叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.77,0:24:04.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きみと離れても　どんなに遠くなっても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:12.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい朝に　あたしは生きるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:20.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}巡って流れて　時は移ろいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:28.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう何があったか　思い出せないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:36.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目を閉じてみれば　誰かの笑い声
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:45.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なぜかそれが今一番の宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:41.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一見面就會吵個不停的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:47.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如今已成為一段難忘的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:56.63,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是你教會了我 不要再去害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:22:09.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無論如何都要抓住幸福 所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:20.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}孤身一人也要前行 哪怕前方遍佈荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:28.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定會帶著你我的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:36.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}茫茫眾生中與你相遇 如此幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:44.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}然而夢醒時分卻發現 你已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:09.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直伴我左右 給我帶來歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:15.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}回憶起這一切 我忽然察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:24.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來到這世上 我已不虛此行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:37.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就好像慶典結束後 只能留下種種不捨揮手告別
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:48.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這段故事伴我前行 無論天涯和海角
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:56.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}定會實現那個幸福的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.77,0:24:04.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕會與你分開 就算海天相隔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:12.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也將迎接那嶄新的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:20.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時光轉逝 歲月變遷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:28.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖已把曾經的故事遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:36.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但只要一閉上眼 就會聽到那熟悉的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:45.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不知為何 這是如今最珍貴的寶物
Comment: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要從誰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後覺得先從由依開始比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在大食堂游擊演唱會上的那個樂隊主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙總是特別活潑  以欺負日向為樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還當上了樂隊的主唱  做著自己喜歡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該已經相當滿足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要我們從後面推她一把
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就能離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贊成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你準備得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  雖然花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「handsonic  version5」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是handsonic  version5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪像是天使  完全是個惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說冷酷的天使要更加邪惡  所以我才做成這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很好啊  很討人厭的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討人厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  很好  真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  還能長對翅膀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要翅膀幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  看上去不是更帥一些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看上去更帥一些才好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才更像天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁她在樂隊練習時出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「收到了其他社團對你們的噪音投訴」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後指著由依這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尤其是你的吉他噪音特別大」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為你的緣故  樂隊死了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因此我要暫時沒收你的吉他」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你就拿走由依的吉他  離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話由依肯定會追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就逃  然後到院子裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡我會假裝衝出來撞到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此同時你就放開吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會接住吉他  你就順勢逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此創造出我和她單獨相處的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準她練習的時候動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.15,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教學樓A棟  空教室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:30.86,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shine days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  由依
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用這種彆扭的節奏唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由依  唱歌和彈奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心做好其中一樣不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣子下去實在太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能這樣  岩澤前輩也是彈唱兼顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為岩澤在這兩方面都很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要求得太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會時又沒冷場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次可是新曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的吉他  樂隊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就看穿了樂隊現在的弱點？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也懂音樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  我還以為大家都沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我要暫時沒收你的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  由依
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她沒追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  沒了吉他後不就好了很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不覺得這樣音域薄了很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有主旋吉他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再加一個伴奏吉他算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂隊的主唱還是得背個吉他才能打動聽眾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底懂不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  這傢伙對尚子發飆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把吉他拿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住  由依！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  拋太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  接住了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前輩救了它啊  從天使手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙上哪去了  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  「混蛋」個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做事還是那麼隨心所欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨心所欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是都當上樂隊的主唱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他也彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點東西遠遠不夠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  還有其他什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想說的話也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  說給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  想做的事情比一般人多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是那個吧  活著的時候沒能做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候  被車子從後面撞到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後身體就癱瘓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都臥床不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人照顧的話根本活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都要依靠我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很對不起她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過電視還是能看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著音樂節目裡的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想要是自己也能那樣該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那現在不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  還有什麼事想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還經常有看棒球轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球的話不是已經在球技大賽上打過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候沒打出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸棒打？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打出全壘打不算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想等樂隊那邊熟練起來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該好好練習下棒球了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要兼顧這兩方面可是非常辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且再問一下  其他還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很流行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…話是這麼說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個世界的人能夠同時兼顧樂隊棒球還有足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說還有嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙  哪個世界的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…她憧憬的全是電視裡看到的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要把她剛才說的都實現也未免太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從方便的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就試試職業摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業摔跤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用什麼招式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,German  suplex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}德式拱橋摔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種誇張的招式怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換成關節技之類能做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,German  suplex
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就那樣著地獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼一副天真的樣子說這麼可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那麼來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我想的要有力氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我這樣的女孩子辦不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  差點就成功了啊  很可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能再來一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去下面有草的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不掉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這可不是在開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  下次一定會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最後一次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  該不會是連後橋都做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做做看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題果然是出在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個  我好幾次差點失去意識都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從後橋的特訓開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話  快做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從沒有做過這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不會這個的話  German  suplex也沒法做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.13,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(320,220)\fad(200,200)}數小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還抖個不停  不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂依然牢牢地扣在腹部上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美  太完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,German  suplex！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…2…3…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噹噹噹  比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事究竟還要持續多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.48,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教學樓  走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一單挑就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  當然得是連過5人的帶球射門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬拉多納哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  TK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道松下五段在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的他不能像我這樣跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  let  me  cry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然了  於是在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山裡  in  the  mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山裡？還真是個和練習跳舞完全沒關係的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那暫時不會回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫忙把我說的人馬上找來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.89,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教學樓C棟  男廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對由理要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使寄來了這樣一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一個女孩子都對付不了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「還敢自稱是男子漢嗎  真是貽笑大方」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「貽笑大方」你竟然會讀這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋治好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算是笨蛋也會讀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「遵照運動員精神」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「讓我來糾正你們那娘娘腔的性格」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放學後在足球場等你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容真是莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是那傢伙寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的天使已經不是以前那個天使了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混雜了亂七八糟的東西才能寫出這麼傻的挑戰書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種蠢事我可不想奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向游離子報告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說要對由理保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和由理說的話  又要演變成一場激烈的戰鬥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這裡寫著遵照運動員精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是要堂堂正正以運動來決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是寫給我們男生的挑戰書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給由理打報告的話  不更顯得我們沒用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就我們5人上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss  you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.38,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}足球場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是由依嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她開始踢球了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了  混球們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  寫信的人是她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是看不慣平時沒什麼用的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  保護好球門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們男生要勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I  kiss  you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向  你守門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閃開  這群呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是差勁的帶球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿是破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  過了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼  野田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁判  剛才那該給紅牌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢  混球們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  TK  音無
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Easy  come  easy  go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here  we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是哪邊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算殺了你也要得分！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的運動員精神到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意關我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺  殺人斷頭台射門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是想殺我還是想射門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽點太多的射門朝我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連過5人完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們竟然輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手只有由依一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高升起  重重摔下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事一定要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然球被搶斷過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有過守門員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像場鬧劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就開始下一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.73,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}棒球場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在開始前先問一下  把球打到哪裡算是全壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是打到圍欄的外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先盡力打打看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是打中了就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準球  用球棒的中心部分來擊球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊球點太偏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次太偏下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉著眼睛怎麼可能打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沒力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然在加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太累了  手的握力也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天再繼續下去也是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫的聲音雖然很響  但擊出的球完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天已經黑了  都看不清球了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要來嗎  真正的棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力揮棒麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都沒做過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  完全沒碰到球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總歸是辦不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了  這個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要為我做這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是你曾想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力到最後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全壘打什麼的只是個開玩笑一般的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒打出全壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讓身體做了這麼多的運動  所以已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都彷彿是在社團活動  太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過嗎  那時我的身體動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  已經全都實現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現？  實現什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體無法動彈時想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性究極的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒法做家務  洗衣服也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那些了  一個人的話什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個光會給別人添麻煩的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰會要我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神真是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的幸福全都奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼前輩  你會和我結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會和你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩根本不瞭解真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實中的  活著的你無論是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會和你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你有什麼殘疾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由依無法走路  站都站不起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了不管你有什麼殘疾的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使無法走路  無法站立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至無法生育
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我也會和你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都陪伴著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡遇到的你  不是由依的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的由依啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在哪裡遇到你  我都會喜歡上你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在六十億分之一的概率下再次相遇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那時候你的身體依舊無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會和你結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會相遇的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為由依一直躺在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個打棒球的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天把你家窗戶給打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我去撿球的時候看見了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊了一會兒  發現我們非常合得來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中我每天都會去你家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也開始照顧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:22:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一直以來都是一個人在照顧我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.82,0:24:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以後打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會等到最後的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟還有那麼多讓人掛念的傢伙留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.08,0:26:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛劈了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.58,0:26:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.67,0:26:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說清楚點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說是影子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.14,0:26:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被剛剛趕來的野田打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有大山一個人的話就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.74,0:26:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼危險
